                <h3>Never trust someone who...</h3>
                <p>
                    Yeah, we always have that friend – I mean, in every group, there’s always that friend who makes
                    those statements that begin with “never…”. “Never do this, never say that,” they always say.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Now, in a very unusual way, I recently found out that God blessed me with this crew of guys I always
                    hang out with. And what’s great is that my crew has no such guy. Like seriously, I have never heard
                    any of my buddies say to me or to any other anything having statements beginning with the N word.
                    Ok, maybe once in a very big while. But the point is, none of buddies is that dude.

                </p>
                <p>
                    I was really happy when I realized that we’ve enjoyed the entire semester, we’ve had all the fun
                    minus our crew having anyone like that.
                </p>
                <p>
